{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"766baa113d","title":"毛泽东转发十军打虎经验的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"35d71fee03","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":2,"articleId":"766baa113d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e07e6e75e8","type":"title","text":"毛泽东转发十军打虎经验的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"4ec8a46962","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"7da5d8eef3","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"e5fc63dc6b","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区、志愿军，并转各级军区和各军：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"33e8efc238","type":"paragraph","text":"十军这个经验很好。原以为没有多少搞头的，回炉再炼，就清出了大批老虎，管理排长，指导员，股长等人许多都是贪污犯。望各军都向十军看齐。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"3e787d1516","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东二月二日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"7618f2e43a","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"ee1ced6232","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区、志愿军，并转各级军区和各军：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"c5a71bd629","type":"paragraph","text":"在打虎阶段，又是十军的成绩最好，请各军和各军分区将十军的成绩和自己的成绩比较一下，立即作出结论来。十军截至二月二日止已捉一千万元以上老虎五十九只，预计还可捉三十只至四十只。十军“无生产无大建筑，过去被认为比较规矩”，尚且查出这多老虎，那些有生产有大建筑，或过去不大守规矩的部队和机关，老虎当然要更多。十军的政策观点也是正确的。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"},{"id":"780a64a9e5","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东二月六日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d"}],"page":{"id":"db91c3154b","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"766baa113d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}